    "description": "!这是Click Painter的试用版本，包含正式版的部分内容。<br><br>点击绘图 是一款需要运用逻辑思维完成谜题，并在轻松愉快的氛围中绘制精美画作的解密游戏。化身画家，挥洒色彩，让你的作品成为挽救阿米美术馆的救世之作！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253820/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.poster.avif?t=1727524045\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253820/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.webm?t=1727524045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253820/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.mp4?t=1727524045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253820/extras/cf878db98e3f7cf62ed6e9b5ae3cbefd.poster.avif?t=1727524045\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253820/extras/cf878db98e3f7cf62ed6e9b5ae3cbefd.webm?t=1727524045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>点击绘图 结合了扫雷的玩法，让你一边解谜一边创作精美画作。每个格子里的数字代表着周围应该有多少相同颜色的颜料。根据这些数字提示，推理出每个格子应该填什么颜料，挥洒出正确的色彩吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253820/extras/79386a8e2b5656b23158a003c115d1b1.poster.avif?t=1727524045\" width=600 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253820/extras/79386a8e2b5656b23158a003c115d1b1.webm?t=1727524045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253820/extras/79386a8e2b5656b23158a003c115d1b1.mp4?t=1727524045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在轻松舒缓的氛围中，按照自己的节奏解谜，你很快就能完成一幅色彩缤纷的画作。无论是可爱的小狗、威武的龙、动听的口琴、俏皮的雪人，还是神秘的魔法师，快来发挥你的创造力，绘制出丰富多彩的画卷吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253820/extras/39862c3502f44c92f864c7cf11b27316.avif?t=1727524045\" width=592 height=300 /></span>",
